comment:
* Captures a planned exercise session, also commonly referred to as a training plan. * *

Each record contains a start time, end time, an exercise type and a list of {@link * PlannedExerciseBlock} which describe the details of the planned session. The start and end times * may be in the future.

methods.name: public int getExerciseType()
methods.comment: Returns the exercise type of this planned session.

methods.name: public CharSequence getNotes()
methods.comment: Returns notes for this planned session. Returns null if it doesn't have notes.

methods.name: public CharSequence getTitle()
methods.comment: Returns title of this planned session. Returns null if it doesn't have a title.

methods.name: public LocalDate getStartDate()
methods.comment: Returns the start date of the planned session.

methods.name: public Duration getDuration()
methods.comment: Returns the expected duration of the planned session.

methods.name: public boolean hasExplicitTime()
methods.comment:
* Returns whether this planned session has an explicit time. If only a date was provided this
     * will be false.

methods.name: public String getCompletedExerciseSessionId()
methods.comment:
* Returns the id of exercise session that completed this planned session. Returns null if none
     * exists.

methods.name: public List<PlannedExerciseBlock> getBlocks()
methods.comment:
* Returns the exercise blocks for this step.
     *
     * @return An unmodifiable list of {@link PlannedExerciseBlock}.
